### ===========================================
### Jobs - Save (Create/Update Job)
### ===========================================

### 1. Create New Job (minimal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/save
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobTitle": "Nuevo Job de Prueba",
    "jobStatus": 6,
    "jobTypeId": 1,
    "jobPriority": 1,
    "jobDescription": "Descripción del job de prueba",
    "jobAddress": "Dirección de prueba"
}

### 2. Create New Job (complete)
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/save
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobTitle": "Job Completo de Prueba",
    "jobStatus": 6,
    "jobTypeId": 1,
    "jobPriority": 2,
    "jobDescription": "Descripción completa del job",
    "jobAddress": "Av. Principal 123, Zona 10",
    "privateCode": "JOB-001",
    "startDate": "2025-12-18T08:00:00",
    "dueDate": "2025-12-18T17:00:00",
    "minTime": 30,
    "maxTime": 120,
    "notificationEmails": "usuario@email.com",
    "userNames": "operador1^operador2",
    "formIds": "1^2^3"
}

### 3. Update Existing Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/Jobs/save
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "jobId": 12345,
    "jobTitle": "Job Actualizado",
    "jobStatus": 6,
    "jobTypeId": 1,
    "jobPriority": 3,
    "jobDescription": "Descripción actualizada del job",
    "jobAddress": "Nueva dirección actualizada",
    "startDate": "2025-12-19T09:00:00",
    "dueDate": "2025-12-19T18:00:00"
}

### ===========================================
### Job Status Reference:
### 0 - Eliminado
### 1 - Activo
### 2 - Pausado
### 3 - Finalizado
### 4 - Incompleto
### 5 - Reprogramado
### 6 - Programado
### 7 - Cancelado
### 8 - Pendiente
### ===========================================

### ===========================================
### Job Priority Reference:
### 1 - Baja
### 2 - Media
### 3 - Alta
### ===========================================

